    "name": "task",
    "purpose": "Owns agent task runtime state. TaskState stores execution_map from ExecutionSignature to StepSignature. task_step.rs routes only complete step events into on_step_complete, waits for PlanQueue::complete_step to report plan completion before running model/execution completion handlers, and renders ExecutionAnalysisPrompt for execution-analysis model steps. task_execution.rs starts execution steps, records execution_map entries, maps succeeding execution status back into StepEvent::Complete, and starts execution-analysis plans from completed execution output.",
